{"tid":409635,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國律師監管當局-曾註冊都應有紀錄-但查無-何君堯-此人/","createTime":"2017-09-22T08:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T09:02:17.000Z","uid":34144,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"874a2e82d40e47b82236c2e5cd95f07b24607867","tid":409635,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:32:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/英國律師監管當局-曾註冊都應有紀錄-但查無-何君堯-此人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E4%BD%86%E6%9F%A5%E7%84%A1-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E6%AD%A4%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=w4d6%2BSG2rwswpfweG4w1KbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=c0a9492b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%9B%A3%E7%AE%A1%E7%95%B6%E5%B1%80-%E6%9B%BE%E8%A8%BB%E5%86%8A%E9%83%BD%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84-%E4%BD%86%E6%9F%A5%E7%84%A1-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF-%E6%AD%A4%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=a4f01124\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/英國律師監管當局-曾註冊都應有紀錄-但查無-何君堯-此人/</a><br />\n<br />\n就今早流傳一封信件，指立法會議員何君堯「英格蘭和威爾士執業律師」資格存疑一事，《立場新聞》致電被指發出信件的英國Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA)。該局職員回覆稱，由於缺乏信件參考編號，無法確認香港流傳的信件真偽（有關信件的參考編號被遮蔽）。不過，該局職員應《立場》記者要求即時翻查「英國和威爾士執業律師」名冊，仍然找不到何君堯的名字。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯早前回覆《立場新聞》及在FB直播解畫時指，自己曾於英國和新加坡兩地註冊，只是沒有執業，故其名字未能在SRA名冊中顯示。不過，SRA職員回覆立場新聞時表示，只要曾經註冊（admitted），無論有否在當地執業，名冊均會有所紀錄，並應有SRA ID number。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》向SRA查詢時，曾要求職員以&quot;Junius Ho Kwan Yiu&quot;、&quot;Ho Kwan Yiu&quot;、&quot;Kwan Yiu Ho&quot;等不同名字查詢，均沒有找到任何紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯去年競選立法會時，在文宣中介紹自己是「新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師」。根據何君堯在「何君柱律師樓」網站及立法會履歷申報，他在1997年成為英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師（Admitted as a Solicitor in England and Wales in 1997）。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》今午再致電何君堯查詢，但暫未能直接聯絡上他，何君堯也暫未回覆記者的留言問題。"},{"pid":"0fc0d847530c61331e9c21ba8898f73bc5e1e87f","tid":409635,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a2cd958f0e86b123ae6f0401a03926b59ae8e5","tid":409635,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605db90ae00211318c37edb8f9d7075b8d11c2a4","tid":409635,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"有巴打post咗,過去集中討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/409636/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/409636/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"fdceec7dc4785dd0274de0652894cec0eb7433cd","tid":409635,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9167b51383b2610110ee6caa9eadc9addb07cae4","tid":409635,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪要人地派人上傳媒爆你講大話呀"},{"pid":"13b7b592112f3c8356c16fd2078690bdd04a1f72","tid":409635,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861bb33e1c81789279096857eb4c9d5d8e4529fe","tid":409635,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}